name: CyberWorld
description: CyberWorld emerges as the fastest auto-compounding protocol in the world of Decentralized Finance. CyberWorld is classified as a native token on the protocol, which also serves as the network's "native currency." The protocol equips RFI properties and is equipped with innovative technologies and features that other forks lack. The CyberWorld platform is specially designed to be automated and extremely efficient. The platform provides users with an 0.018% increase in their assets every 10 minutes. All rebase interests are paid in "$CyberWorld token" along with many other utilities, also providing the facility of protocol governance.
